@startuml C2_events_read
title C2. 이벤트 목록/상세 조회

actor User
participant "app-service" as SVC
database "PostgreSQL\n(Event)" as PG

== 목록 ==
User -> SVC: GET /api/events?sort=latest&page=1&size=20&tag=전시
SVC -> PG: SELECT ... FROM events WHERE tag=... ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT/OFFSET
SVC --> User: 200 OK {success:true, data:[...]}

== 상세 ==
User -> SVC: GET /api/events/{id}
SVC -> PG: SELECT * FROM events WHERE id=...
alt 미존재
  SVC --> User: 404 NOT_FOUND
  return
end
SVC --> User: 200 OK {success:true, data:{...}}
@enduml
